ax\b0 \highlight\uc2  and luxury \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  on local-made products, was not helping local industries. \par \par \uc2  Soy said that other internal problems included the weak legal environment, the poor implementation of the regional autonomy \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  and the \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertain\b0 \highlight\uc2  business climate. \par \par \uc2  Kadin has been actively organizing meetings and conferences with local industries and business associations to examine their preparations in anticipating AFTA. \par \par \uc2  The result of these programs will be submitted as input for the government. \par \par \uc2  "We have submitted the facts to the chief \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  minister and the trade and industry minister," Soy said \par \par \uc2  "It now depends on what the government will decide about the findings," he added. \par \par \uc2  Copyright 2001 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020011219dxck00067\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
