ces have been exploited by profiteers through the smuggling of cheap fuel overseas. \par \par \uc2  Nevertheless, the supervision mechanism will have to be improved steadily so as to ensure smooth fuel distribution and that the Rp2.8 trillion in compensation funds will fully reach the targeted poor families. - The Jakarta Post \par \par \uc2  OIL PRICE HIKE ANNOUNCED \par \par \uc2  The government has finally announced the increase in oil prices \par \par \uc2  on Thursday but there were no long queues in gas stations as before. \par \par \uc2  We have heard however that university students in Bandung (West \par \par \uc2  Java) and Makassar (South Sulawesi) had staged protests against the government move. But if we understand the condition of the state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 , we must accept the government's decision. \par \par \uc2  The government provides the oil sector an annual \b \highlight22\uc2 subsidy\b0 \highlight\uc2  of Rp 66 trillion. The \b \highlight22\uc2 subsidy\b0 \highlight\uc2  however has only been taken advantage of by the rich, who have many luxurious cars. \par \par \uc2  Nevertheless, the government should not wash its hands after announcing the new oil prices. It must anticipate the impact of the new oil prices on other commodities. The government should control the market so as not to make the prices of other commodities become unreasonable. \par \par \uc2  One important thing the government has to do is to decide how to use the Rp 2.85 trillion \b \highlight22\uc2 subsidy\b0 \highlight\uc2  it would be able to save from the oil price hike. \par \par \uc2  The people might get very angry if the remaining \b \highlight22\uc2 subsidy\b0 \highlight\uc2  is \par \par \uc2  channeled only to certain people or groups like businessmen. \par \par \uc2  If we do not want to cooperate with one another, the coming days \par \par \uc2  would be difficult ones. - Kompas. \par \par \uc2 Document antara0020020122dy1i000gq\par }\page