\par\par \b \uc2  MONDAY'S EDITORIALS IN INDONESIAN MAJOR DAILIES. \b0\par\par\uc2 732 \uc2 words\par \uc2 18 March 2002\par \uc2 ANTARA - The Indonesian National News Agency\par \uc2 ANTARA\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2002 Asia Pulse Pte Limited. Asia Pulse gives no warranty or guarantee as to the accuracy of the information, Asia Pulse shall not be liable for errors or omissions in, or delays or interruptions to or cessation of delivery of, the data through its negligence or otherwise.\par \par \uc2  TODAY, THE FORMING OF THE SPECIAL INVESTIGATION COMMITTEE ON BULOGGATE II WILL BE DECIDED \par \par \uc2  All factions of the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2  (DPR) must have decided by now whether or not to form a special committee to probe into the misuse of State Logistics Agency (Bulog) funds worth Rp 40 billion, where House Speaker Akbar Tandjung is a suspect. Like waiting for the last voice of a house lizard, we want to know the answer: is it "yes" or "no"? Or, will the final decision be postponed again? \par \par \uc2  Meanwhile, the legal process goes on. Some people say the process is running fast. The dossiers of Tandjung, who was state secretary when the misuse occurred, has been handed to the Jakarta Attorney's Office and even passed to the Central Jakarta district court. Within the coming days, the trial proceeding for the Bulog case will be decided. \par \par \uc2  How far is our socio-political and socio-security resistance and capability lead us to a clearer and firmer future which can free us from the traps and complexities of the past? \par \par \uc2  Ideally, what we must have is a gradual but fair and consistent process in which we can all remind and correct one another. If this needs a special committee, please go ahead and form it. We should be responsible together. - Kompas \par \par \uc2  FARALLON WINS BANK BCA \par \par \uc2  By selecting Farallon Capital Management of the United States as winner of 51 percent of Bank Central Asia (BCA) over the favorite, Standard Chartered Bank of Britain, last week, the government decided to give higher priority to the credibility and fairness of the transaction over the integrity, competence and reputation of the investor. \par \par \uc2  But then the transaction is no longer a strategic sale in the real sense because the "strategic" component that was supposed to be brought in by the new investor's high integrity, competence and reputation in the banking industry was missing. \par \par \uc2  What the bidding process produced was the Farallon - Djarum consortium, the strange coupling of an investment firm with a cigarette maker. \par \par \uc2  BCA's main weakness is poor risk management and credit assessment. Farallon's success will depend on how far and how long it will tap Deutche Bank's resources for developing BCA human resources. \par \par \uc2  Yet, we are still worried until the detailed-shareholding structure of the Farallon-Djarum consortium and the terms and conditions of the sale and purchase contract disclosed. \par \par \uc2  The market would be nervous if the majority owner were the Djarum group - rumored to have bought 14 percent of BCA through the stock market - as the \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  is still traumatized by the 1998 banking crisis, caused mostly by conglomerate-owned banks. - The Jakarta Post \par \par \uc2  FIREBALL OF SPECIAL INVESTIGATION COMMITTEE ON BULOGGATE II \par \par \uc2  People can only presume what will happen today (Monday) at the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of\b0 \highlight\b \highlight22\uc2 Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2 . Thousands of demonstrators are likely to take to the streets to march to the \b \highlight22\uc2 legislative\b0 \highlight\uc2  assembly building. They consist of supporters and opponents of the move to form a House's special committee to probe the misuse of Rp 40 billion in State Logistics Agency (Bulog) funds. Inside the House, factions play their roles in pushing for or rejecting the formation of the special committee. \par \par \uc2      Today's (Monday's) House plenary session will decide whether or \par \par \uc2  not to form the committee. \par \par \uc2      Whether or not the investigation committee will be formed, the \par \par \uc2  political fireball will keep on moving. In the coming days, political tension will escalate until the convening of the People's Consultative Assembly's (MPR) annual meeting in September. This is due to the fact that politics in the country has been designed for the sake of sacking (political rivals), seeking opportunities and revenge. \par \par \uc2  Politics has placed this nation in a trap of prolonged \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2 . The people's representatives are more interested in the power struggle than in seeking ways to eradicate poverty, unemployment, \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2 , and insecurity. The government, which has the task to make its people prosperous, is more interested in defending its power. \par \par \uc2  The executive and \b \highlight22\uc2 legislative\b0 \highlight\uc2  branches of government have this nation in their hands. On behalf of the people, they feel that they are the most righteous party to decide what is black and what is white in this nation. Those in the executive and \b \highlight22\uc2 legislative\b0 \highlight\uc2  bodies do not care whether the people eat or are happy or are disgusted with political practices. - Republika. \par \par \uc2 Document antara0020020320dy3i00002\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
