 well as principal on some of its $140 billion debts. \par \par \uc2  "We think the terms we have got are much better than what we got in previous Paris Club rounds," Indonesia's Chief \b \highlight22\uc2 Economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  Minister Dorodjatun Kuntjoro-Jakti told reporters in Paris. \par \par \uc2  "We hope this will alleviate the pressure on the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  and balance of payments for this year and next but there are still \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainties\b0 \highlight\uc2 , notably the price of oil and the yen-to-dollar exchange rate," he said. \par \par \uc2  Jakarta needs the rescheduling to help cut its 2002 \b \highlight22\uc2 budget deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  and reduce balance of payment risks. \par \par \uc2  Copyright 2002 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020020415dy4e0005u\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
